program to display zmanim as a screensaver for kindle (KT4). (old commits for K4NT)

kzman executes it.

ran with argument delta sets the rtc to wakeup and refresh the screensaver on day change.

the scripts in ./utils/ create the backround pictures.

the scripts in ./zman/ are used on the kindle to run the program and start an boot.
